 @Test
    void testCashAllocationModels_SpecificLines() throws ParseException {
        // Create a test line that triggers the logic in lines 746-775
        String line = "");

        List<String> lines = new ArrayList<>();
        lines.add(validLine);

        // Mock supplementaryDetailsService.getInvoiceRefFromSupplementaryDetails
        when(supplementaryDetailsService.getInvoiceRefFromSupplementaryDetails(anyString()))
                .thenReturn("INV-REF-123");

        // Call the method
        List<CashAllocationModel> result = cashAllocationDomain.cashAllocationModelList(lines, "testFile.txt");

        // Assert the result
        assertEquals(1, result.size());
        CashAllocationModel model = result.get(0);
        assertEquals("INV-REF-123", model.getInvoiceRef());
        assertEquals(new SimpleDateFormat("yyyyMMdd", Locale.US).parse("20231027"), model.getValueDate());
        assertEquals(new BigDecimal("10.00"), model.getAmount());
        assertEquals("0123456789", model.getTransactionNumber());
    }
